Richemont Brands to Create Jobs in Switzerland, Le Temps Says

-- B y   D e r m o t   D o h e r t y
-- 
2011-12-02T08:29:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-02/richemont-brands-to-create-jobs-in-switzerland-le-temps-says.html
Cie. Financiere Richemont SA (CFR) ’s
Panerai and Cartier brands may hire more employees in
 Switzerland , Le Temps reported.  Watchmaker Panerai may create 120 jobs at a new plant in
Neuchatel, the newspaper reported, without saying where it got
the information. Jeweler  Cartier  also plans to hire more people
in the same canton, Le Temps said, citing the company. The brand
said it’s still to be decided how many jobs will be created,
according to the newspaper.  -- Editors: Thomas Mulier, Robert Valpuesta  To contact the reporter on this story:
